      <body>
         <div>
            <head>Translated parts</head>
            <p xml:id="KR2e0001-start">
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:05:56.873+09:00">Lord Wu attacked Yi,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:11:55.104+09:00">killed Marquis Ai [of Jin],</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:12:01.305+09:00">stopped Luan Gongzi and said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:12:42.639+09:00">"If you do not die, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:13:55.445+09:00">I will take you to visit the Son of Heaven</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:15:20.502+09:00">I will mandate you to become minister,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:17:20.179+09:00">and to take control of Jin's government."</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:16:11.081+09:00">[Luan Gongzi] refused and said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:22:02.506+09:00">"I have heard that 'Man is brought up by three,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:22:07.905+09:00">'Man is brought up by three,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:23:54.666+09:00">and serves them as if they were one.'</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:25:00.962+09:00">The father begets him,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:26:07.721+09:00">the teacher educates him,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T05:35:09.989+09:00">                                    and the ruler feeds him.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:52:59.633+09:00">                                    Without a father, he would not live;</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:53:29.443+09:00">without food, he would not grow up;</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T05:27:54.864+09:00">                                    He is raised by many,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:43:36.531+09:00">and therefore serves them equally.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T18:40:33.269+09:00">                                    Whoever he relies on,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T18:47:17.426+09:00">                                    he will die for.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T05:29:52.971+09:00">To repay life with death,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T05:30:02.802+09:00">                                    and to repay gifts with diligence</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:56:11.374+09:00">                                    this is the way of man.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T04:53:27.403+09:00">without education, he would not understand.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T05:07:00.606+09:00">If I, your servant, discarded the way of man for personal profit,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T05:30:32.297+09:00">                                    how could you, my lord, demand loyalty [from others]?</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T05:31:55.549+09:00">                                    Besides, if you know that I will comply,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T05:16:09.979+09:00">you will still not know that I will serve [you] at Quwo.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T05:33:24.809+09:00">                                    If a man follows a ruler and thereby betrays another,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T05:32:58.341+09:00">                                    how could the ruler trust him?"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-2a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T05:33:32.963+09:00">                                    He then fought and died.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="wilke" modified="2019-11-28T05:25:41.711+09:00">Lord Wu [of Jin] attacks Yi and stops Luan Gongzi from killing himself</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T19:04:44.034+09:00">                                    Lord Xian [of Jin] divined about an attack on the Li barbarians,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T19:05:50.638+09:00">The scribe Su read the cracks</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T19:05:57.516+09:00">and said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T00:40:21.994+09:00">                                    "[The attack] will be victorious but not beneficial."</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T19:09:30.049+09:00">The Lord asked:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T19:09:45.263+09:00">"What do you mean?"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T19:09:58.326+09:00">[Su] answered:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T09:29:19.49+09:00">                                                                        "We encountered a crack,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T09:29:35.283+09:00">it takes hold by biting on the bone, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T09:29:49.391+09:00">                                    the teeth are in disarray.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T09:00:29.556+09:00">The barbarians and the Xia will take turns to strike.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T00:35:14.286+09:00">                                    To take turns to strike</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T00:35:22.594+09:00">                                    is to take turns to win.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T19:36:11.559+09:00">That is why I said it.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T22:39:28.636+09:00">                                    Moreover, I fear that there will be a mouth</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T22:42:32.027+09:00">                                    that will lead the people astray,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T22:43:57.888+09:00">                                    and because of which [the men of] the country will change their hearts.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T19:47:12.324+09:00">The Lord said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T19:51:17.153+09:00">The mouth is with me, the solitary man.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T22:15:37.889+09:00">If I do not accept it,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T22:35:10.375+09:00">"What mouth?</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T00:39:10.102+09:00">                                    who will dare to deploy it [against me]?"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T22:42:57.072+09:00">[Su] answered:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T23:10:37.232+09:00">“If [the people] can be led astray,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T00:55:03.803+09:00">                                    the words that they hand in will be sweet.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T00:55:28.407+09:00">                                    If you succumb to their flattery and are fooled,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T23:29:25.522+09:00">how could you stop them?"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T23:30:06.263+09:00">The lord did not listen,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T23:30:49.868+09:00">attacked the Li barbarians,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T23:31:04.631+09:00">and defeated them.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T00:55:45.415+09:00">                                    He obtained Li Ji and took her home,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T00:55:57.527+09:00">He favored her</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-28T23:34:31.102+09:00">and made her his wife.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:20:32.459+09:00">The Lord drank ale with the grandees.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:20:47.215+09:00">and ordered the ritual overseer to fill a cup to give it to the scribe Su.  </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:16:00.955+09:00">He said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:17:15.058+09:00">"Drink and empty it. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:17:57.979+09:00">As for before my campaign against the Li barbarians</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:18:08.172+09:00">you said,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:21:38.379+09:00">'It will be victorious but not beneficial.'</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:21:38.749+09:00">Therefore, I reward you with a cup [of ale]</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:51:59.784+09:00">and punish you by making you emptying it.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:51:59.106+09:00">To defeat a country and obtain a concubine,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:51:58.198+09:00">what could be more beneficial!"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:51:57.382+09:00">The scribe Su finished the cup,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:51:56.536+09:00">bowed again and said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:51:55.758+09:00">"The crack was there, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T05:32:58.346+09:00">                                     I, your servant, did not dare to conceal it.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T05:42:53.546+09:00">                                    To conceal the crack's instructions,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T05:43:06.358+09:00">and to neglect my office:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T05:29:53.957+09:00">I would have been punished twice for this.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.53" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:52:34.399+09:00">How could I have served you?</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.54" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:53:23.562+09:00">The great punishment will come</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.55" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:53:43.911+09:00">and it will not be the emptying of a cup.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.56" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T05:45:23.196+09:00">                                    I urge you to prepare for the ominous consequences of your campaign while enjoying its benefits.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.57" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:58:10.28+09:00">If there will not be any ominous consequences,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.58" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T01:59:47.14+09:00">what damage could the preparations do?</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.59" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T02:00:05.998+09:00">If there will be ominous consequences,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.60" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T05:46:32.575+09:00">                                    the preparations will be your cure.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.62" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T02:05:37.479+09:00">would be a blessing for the country,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.63" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T02:05:40.67+09:00">why would I dare to fear punishment?"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-4a.61" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T02:06:04.918+09:00">My untrustworthiness</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T05:48:14.459+09:00">[The lord] drank the ale and went outside.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T05:47:52.425+09:00">The scribe Su told the grandees:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T05:48:52.906+09:00">"If there are male barbarians, there must be female barbarians.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T05:49:51.748+09:00">If Jin defeats the barbarians with male barbarians,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T05:52:37.919+09:00">then the barbarians must certainly defeat Jin with female barbarians,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T06:00:13.092+09:00">what can we do!"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T06:00:37.223+09:00">Li Ke asked:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T06:00:57.019+09:00">"What do you mean?"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T06:01:40.334+09:00">The scribe Su said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:00:01.729+09:00">"In the past when Jie of Xia attacked Youshi,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T06:06:27.362+09:00">the people of Youshi made Mo Xi his woman.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T06:06:42.217+09:00">Mo Xi was favored</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T06:58:50.907+09:00">and thereupon she collaborated with Yi Yin and destroyed Xia.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:02:32.159+09:00">When Xin of Yin attacked Yousu,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:02:26.264+09:00">the Yousu made Daji his woman.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:02:54.4+09:00">Daji was favored,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:03:53.578+09:00">and thereupon she collaborated with Jiao Ge and destroyed Shang.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:04:27.434+09:00">When King You of Zhou attacked Youbao,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:05:19.473+09:00">the people of Bao made Bao Si his wife.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:05:27.98+09:00">Bao Si was favored,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:07:14.156+09:00">she gave birth to Bofu,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:09:54.664+09:00">and thereupon she collaborated with Guo Shifu,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:11:24.023+09:00">banished the heir apparent Yijiu and made Bofu the heir to the throne.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:13:00.873+09:00">The heir apparent left the country and fled to Shen. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:13:30.075+09:00">The people of Shen</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:14:35.333+09:00">and Zeng summoned the western barbarians to attack Zhou</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:15:04.755+09:00">and thereupon Zhou vanished.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:21:00.319+09:00">Now Jin has little power and is hospitable towards female prisoners of war,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:22:37.947+09:00">if he increases his favor even more,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:26:39.404+09:00">                                    assuming he were a king of the three dynasties,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:30:26.954+09:00">would it not still be wrong?</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T09:27:32.259+09:00">                                    Besides, the crack says:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T09:25:10.517+09:00">                                    the teeth are in disarray.'</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T09:25:12.183+09:00">                                                                        'It takes hold by biting on the bone,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:40:06.563+09:00">I divined about the attack on the Li,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:43:59.319+09:00">                                    the plastron responded to us with 'set out'</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-29T07:46:31.083+09:00">and 'disband'.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T08:12:38.835+09:00">In the case this is correct,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T08:13:20.904+09:00">it is a sign for malice.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T08:22:50.139+09:00">This is not my guesswork (度),</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T08:22:49.05+09:00">when [the country] falls apart, it will happen.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T08:32:31.705+09:00">If it will not take control over the country,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T08:42:34.533+09:00">could it be said to 'take hold'?</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T08:42:43.243+09:00">If it will not reach the ruler,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T08:42:45.443+09:00">can it 'bite on the bone'?</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T08:44:06.743+09:00">Assuming that it will take control of the country and reach the ruler, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T09:14:35.068+09:00">                                    even if it encounters the teeth,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-12-03T07:22:22.695+09:00">                                                                                                            by disarraying half of them,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T09:19:48.118+09:00">                                    who will say that he will not comply?</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T09:19:47.259+09:00">If the Xia comply with the barbarians,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T09:19:46.451+09:00">what is this but a defeat?</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.53" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T09:19:45.541+09:00">Those who govern must be cautious,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-5a.54" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-11-30T09:19:43.505+09:00">the end is only days away.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-12-03T07:24:46.037+09:00">Guo Yan said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-12-03T07:56:30.67+09:00">"As for the fall of three dynasties: it was supposed to happen.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-12-03T07:29:45.394+09:00">If the ruler of the people</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-12-03T07:43:22.875+09:00">succumbs to infatuation without feeling bad about it,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-12-03T07:43:20.699+09:00">if his indulgence in pomp has no end,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-12-03T07:47:22.119+09:00">if he gives free rein to his will</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-12-03T07:47:34.073+09:00">and does not feel bad about anything,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-12-03T07:54:57.194+09:00">then he will fall to ruin and obtain the chance to learn from the past.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-12-03T07:58:25.456+09:00">Today the lands of Jin</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-12-03T07:58:39.62+09:00">are a remote fiefdom.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-12-03T08:02:08.143+09:00">Not only is its territory small,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2019-12-03T08:03:24.772+09:00">but its neighboring countries are vast.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T19:37:19.916+09:00">                                    Although [its ruler] is about to succumb to infatuation,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T19:57:09.284+09:00">it has never obtained sole control.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T19:40:35.274+09:00">The powerful noble families [of Jin]</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T19:56:46.979+09:00">                                                                        and the neighboring countries will raise and protect it,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T19:56:07.231+09:00">they will repeatedly appoint it a new ruler, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T19:56:16.053+09:00">it will not accumulate into vanishment.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T19:56:22.921+09:00">Although new rulers will be appointed, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-6a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T19:56:24.929+09:00">there will be no more than five.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T20:54:02.928+09:00">"Oh, grand masters, be warned,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2021-11-09T03:50:47.226+09:00">the root of chaos is growing!</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T20:58:42.664+09:00">The scribe Su entered the court</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T20:58:53.391+09:00">and told the grand masters saying:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2021-11-09T03:56:49.012+09:00">When, some time ago, our lord made Li Ji his wife,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2021-11-09T04:06:29.798+09:00">the contempt all people had for him was certainly already extreme.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:19:00.119+09:00">so that they could find delight in them. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:19:16.784+09:00">Therefore, there was no one who did not prove his loyalty and was full of zeal to rush to his death.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:26:27.177+09:00">Today our lord is raising the people to enfeoff himself,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:29:54.449+09:00">and inwardly they abhor his greed,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:32:05.476+09:00">top and bottom are therefore already divided;</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:33:45.811+09:00">if that’s not the way of Heaven?!</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:33:47.071+09:00">Thento have another boy, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:34:27.585+09:00">Heaven has strengthened his poison,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:34:45.516+09:00">the people hate his attitude,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:35:18.631+09:00">chaos will arise!</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:37:02.589+09:00">I have heard that a nobleman loves good and detests evil,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:42:36.352+09:00">enjoys happiness and finds peace in stability,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:43:22.246+09:00">andthus achieves to last forever.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:58:48.779+09:00">If atree is not cut down at its root, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:58:50.602+09:00">it will grow again;</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T21:58:56.105+09:00">If water at is not stopped at its source,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:05:43.876+09:00">it will flow again;</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:05:44.189+09:00">If calamity is not exterminated at its base,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:05:44.728+09:00">it will cause chaos again.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:05:18.188+09:00">Today our lord has killed her father and feeds her son, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:05:23.83+09:00">this is the base of calamity. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:05:25.747+09:00">He feeds her son and also follows her requests,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:05:54.631+09:00">and also follows her requests,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:10:47.351+09:00">A son takes revenge for the shame of his father and follows his requests faithfully, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:16:15.453+09:00">If he is lewd,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:16:22.921+09:00">the son must abhor it inwardly, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:16:25.122+09:00">and must not approve of it. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:20:47.254+09:00">If he approves of it,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:25:13.284+09:00">hewill suffer from [his father’s] desires. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:29:04.318+09:00">If one tries to fulfill the desires of someone else by rewarding his wishes, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:32:25.955+09:00">and listens to his hideous heart,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:32:25.216+09:00">then he will ruin the country,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:32:23.85+09:00">and deepen the chaos.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:33:56.399+09:00">The chaos will certainly originate with the barbarian women, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:41:08.559+09:00">as it was with each of the Three Dynasties."</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:39:10.766+09:00">Li Ji did indeed cause difficulties. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:39:11.046+09:00">She killed the first-born son and expelled the other two sons of the lord. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:40:58.624+09:00">The noble man says:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:40:48.451+09:00">"Recognize difficulties at their root." </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2021-11-09T04:06:37.807+09:00">In past campaigns,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:42:35.427+09:00">the people were mobilized for the sake of the people,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-11a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="crone.thomas" modified="2020-02-14T22:42:50.974+09:00">Externally,the people cannot benefit,</seg>
            <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_001-57a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-04-21T18:25:05.107+09:00">would I dare to care most for my own safety?</seg></p>
         </div>
